811dd8d1-40a5-4bee-ad7e-d51cc8014c26	people	38df7599-eac0-4611-aa2b-1902e7dfc93b	bio	""	"For 30+ years Tom Truss has been a performer, creator, and educator. His work has appeared from the Kennedy Center to the Wellington Fringe Festival. He has an MFA in Acting and another in Dance. He is certified in the Alexander Technique and Internal Family Systems, and is currently touring 3 shows: Tell Me What You Learned Tuesday, Tipsy MacBoozle, and ReWritten."	fb137e07-9006-47a3-9492-f4c155c31313	bio_csv_import	2026-02-23 19:12:22.795779+00
